Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,派遣到职业现场去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.95,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,并且要留下可见实绩的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,实地研修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:13.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个试炼正进入白热化阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:17.01,shiki Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs105\pos(1023,621)}试开业 最后一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(807,1011)}suer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,出水的时机不对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢等不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,细心地想象蔬菜出水的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.22,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.51,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好好记住这个表面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:27.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法国菜真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.56,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和传统的日本料理的思考方式完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:35.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本料理一般倾向于不加工食材
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:40.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能地让原材料保持原汁原味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:44.37,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,相反法国菜会花费大量的时间和功夫加工食材
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.20,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,光是制作高汤就很费时了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.33,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,与日本料理的昆布高汤是完全不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:56.25,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,阿贝尔还真是悉心教导呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:58.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你连法国菜的基础都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:00.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:01.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:04.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要制作的鱼料理配方都记清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.10,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.18,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,800;446,{\frz3.522\move(1200,669,975,666)}poêler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.18,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,976;440,{\frz2.431\move(1464,660,1236,660)}油煎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:09.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:10.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,准备的怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的比赛想好做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上是决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:17.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是差点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:19.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是最后一天也不要疏忽大意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:23.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:24.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,1002)}oui chef
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:24.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:28.33,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我一定会做出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.37,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我才能创造出的「必杀料理」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------OP------------------
